import { Paper, Avatar, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

function SearchCards() {
    return (
        <Paper style={{width: "25%", height: "30%"}}>
            <Avatar>T</Avatar>
            <Typography align="center" varient="h1">Ed Revalo</Typography>
            <Typography align="center">Department</Typography>
            <Typography align="center">Company</Typography>
            <Typography align="center">Job Title</Typography>
        </Paper>
    )
}

export default SearchCards
